{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_河边递纸",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·河边递纸（镜像恐怖）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "narrative": "scenario_河边",
              "state": "fled",
              "reached": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "河滩上雾还没散。他下意识摸了摸怀里那几张纸钱——快走吧。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "回程，河滩。雾压着水面，黄昏的光淌不进来。走到半道，关二狗肚子一阵绞——他钻进芦苇丛后头，蹲下了。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（……纸。纸啊。出门忘带纸了。）",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    "n3": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_河边递纸",
            "signal": "hebian_handed"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n4"
    },
    "n4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "身后，伸过来一只手。递来一沓纸钱——黄的，软的，分量正好。",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「哎，多谢哥。」（顺手接了）",
          "next": "c1_a"
        },
        {
          "id": "leng",
          "text": "（愣了一下……还是接了）",
          "next": "c1_b"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c1_a": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他接得那叫一个自然，还客气地道了声谢，扯了几张用了。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "c1_b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "手比脑子快。等纸已经到了手里，他才想起来该说声谢——也说了。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    "n5": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_河边递纸",
            "signal": "hebian_took"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n6"
    },
    "n6": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（…………等等。）",
      "next": "n7"
    },
    "n7": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（前不着村，后不着店。这河滩上——哪来的人？？）",
      "next": "n8"
    },
    "n8": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_河边递纸",
            "signal": "hebian_realized"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n9"
    },
    "n9": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "猛回头——没人。雾里空荡荡，远处水声哗哗。手里，还攥着剩下的纸钱。",
      "next": "n10"
    },
    "n10": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "当年他蹲在旁边看人出恭、看人窘迫还嘻嘻笑。如今轮到他蹲着，一只手客客气气递来纸——那东西规规矩矩的，把他当「自家人」。",
      "next": "n11"
    },
    "n11": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_河边递纸",
            "signal": "hebian_fled"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n12"
    },
    "n12": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（有东西……在跟着俺。）",
      "next": "n13"
    },
    "n13": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他提着裤子一路小跑回城。那几张没用完的纸钱，扔也不是，留也不是，最后还是揣进了怀里——扔了，不吉利。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}